perturbation.original_text:
FCC warrants to Flotek that:

(a) all of the Terpene Product supplied by FCC to Flotek shall:

(i) conform to the specifications set forth in Section 1;

(ii) comply with all relevant laws and regulations including, without limitation, laws and regulations of each of the jurisdictions in which the Terpene Product are either manufactured or to be sold or used concerning purity, sanitation, safety, security, and packaging and labeling of food and beverage;

(iii) be in good condition at the time of delivery in all respects; and

(iv) be free from any defect in design, workmanship, materials and packaging;

(b) it shall convey to Flotek good title to the Terpene Product free of any encumbrance, lien or security interest;

perturbation.changed_text:
FCC warrants to Flotek that:

(a) most of the Terpene Product supplied by FCC to Flotek may:

(i) conform to the general specifications referenced in Section 1;

(ii) comply with general laws and regulations including, laws and regulations of each of the jurisdictions in which the Terpene Product are either manufactured or to be sold or used concerning purity, sanitation, safety, security, and packaging and labeling of food and beverage;

(iii) be in acceptable condition at the time of delivery; and

(iv) be free from any significant defect in design, workmanship, materials and packaging;

(b) it shall convey to Flotek questionable title to the Terpene Product free of significant encumbrance, lien or security interest;
